7:["$","article",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-white","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12","children":[["$","header",null,{"className":"mb-8","children":[["$","h1",null,{"className":"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4","children":"Benefits of 5S technique in implementing ISO 9001"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-center gap-4 text-gray-600","children":[["$","time",null,{"dateTime":"2026-01-02T06:32:15+00:00","children":"January 2, 2026"}],["$","span",null,{"className":"inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 rounded-full text-sm","children":"general"}]]}]]}],null,["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 p-4 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-blue-500","children":["$","p",null,{"className":"text-gray-700 italic","children":"The first and foremost advantage of 5S implementation in your organization is the creation of brand new sources to trace down and rectify work area"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-8 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed","children":[["$","p","0",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Benefits of 5S technique in implementing ISO 9001"}],["$","p","1",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"The first and foremost advantage of 5S ISO 9001 implementation in your organization is the creation of brand new sources to trace down and rectify work area inefficiencies. The problems and issues are brought to light at every monthly or quarterly meeting and goals are set to enhance the overall organization's efficiency. Capturing photographs before and after the implementation of both 5S principles and ISO 9001 QMS standard as well as images of workplace conditions and records of every employee’s routine tasks and task times can facilitate to assess the success of the 5S program in your organization."}],["$","p","2",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Organization located in the industrial work area or surroundings is never improved through work-flow and physical design alone. This is often where the 5S principle (sort, set in order, shine, standardize, sustain) comes into play to organize this area of your organization. 5S could be an operating tool for ISO 9001 QMS certification implementation that was developed to assist managers and work for personnel consistently accomplish goals to make an organization greater, standardization, efficacy and most important safety in the workplace which is the ultimate aim of ISO 45001 certification."}],["$","p","3",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"In order to successfully implement both ISO 9001 certification and 5S technique, it is quite crucial to get started with the process typically requires the formation of an enclosed committee of 5S team leaders. This team is delegated to manage all technique pertaining to “sort” through “sustain.” Depending on the size of the organization, the committee could also be as little as one individual or comprised of many 5S team leaders who come across from all platforms of management, superordinate and designation levels to actively promote 5S principle from its inception."}],["$","p","4",{"className":"mb-6 text-justify leading-8","children":"Once an organization has developed a proper set up or strategies for implementation, those teams and system should move forward with the process. With these kinds of practices, all the workers will be inspired and encouraged to actively participate in the implementation process of the 5S technique. This needs corrective actions and training on how implementation can improve their workplaces. This in turn additionally refine every individual’s role and describe the advantages of 5S."}],"$L10","$L11","$L12","$L13","$L14","$L15","$L16","$L17","$L18","$L19","$L1a","$L1b","$L1c","$L1d","$L1e","$L1f","$L20","$L21","$L22","$L23","$L24","$L25","$L26","$L27","$L28","$L29","$L2a","$L2b"]}],"$L2c"]}]}]
